
---


@startuml

' Entities
class Cinema {
  - id: int
  - name: String
  - town: String
}

class Theatre {
  - id: int
  - name: String
  - capacity: int
  - cinema: Cinema
}

class Movie {
  - id: int
  - title: String
  - duration: int (minutes)
}

class Copy {
  - id: int
  - movie: Movie
  - cinema: Cinema
}

class Show {
  - id: int
  - date: Date
  - startTime: Time
  - endTime: Time
  - theatre: Theatre
  - copy: Copy
  - status: String (e.g., "published", "cancelled")
}

class Reservation {
  - id: int
  - customerEmail: String
  - show: Show
  - seatsReserved: List<Seat>
  - reservationTime: DateTime
  - paymentProcessed: boolean
  - status: String ("confirmed", "cancelled", "expired")
}

class Seat {
  - id: int
  - row: int
  - number: int
  - theatre: Theatre
}

class Ticket {
  - id: int
  - show: Show
  - seat: Seat
  - isOnline: boolean
  - issuedAt: DateTime
}

class Customer {
  - email: String
  - firstName: String
  - lastName: String
}

class Offer {
  - id: int
  - reservation: Reservation
  - newShow: Show
  - newSeats: List<Seat>
  - expirationTime: DateTime
  - status: String ("pending", "accepted", "declined", "expired")
}

class FreeTicket {
  - id: int
  - customerEmail: String
  - reason: String
  - sentDate: Date
}

class AvailabilityDisplay {
  - theatre: Theatre
  - show: Show
  - availableSeats: int
}

' Relationships

Cinema "1" -- "many" Theatre : contains
Theatre "1" -- "many" Show : hosts
Theatre "1" -- "many" Seat : has
Theatre "1" -- "1" AvailabilityDisplay : displayed in

Movie "1" -- "many" Copy : stored in
Copy "1" -- "many" Show : used in

Show "1" -- "many" Reservation : reserved for
Show "1" -- "many" Ticket : tickets for

Reservation "1" -- "many" Offer : offers for
Offer "1" -- "1" Reservation : relates to
Offer "1" -- "1" Show : new show in
Offer "1" -- "many" Seat : new seats for

Reservation "1" -- "many" Seat : reserves
Ticket "1" -- "1" Seat : assigned to

Customer "1" -- "many" Reservation : made by
Customer "1" -- "many" FreeTicket : receives

' Additional associations
FreeTicket "1" -- "1" Show : related to

@enduml

---

### 📌 Notes:
- The `status` fields are examples and can be expanded as needed.
- All associations reflect business rules from the requirements.
- Anonymous ticketing at the entrance is modeled with the `Ticket` class having an `isOnline` flag and no link to `Customer`.
- The `AvailabilityDisplay` is a conceptual class representing the real-time display of available seats.

